---
title: Eggplant and Sun-dried Tomato Linguine with Fresh Mozzarella and Parsley
description: Who has time for hours of stovetop simmering? Get all the flavor in less than half the time by adding sun-dried tomatoes to your sauce. Toss in roasted eggplant, fresh herbs, and a dash of spice for good measure and you’ve got yourself a meat-free crowd pleaser.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/eggplant-and-sun-dried-tomato-linguine-48544fb4.jpg
